[I] Orbit reconstruction, simulation and analysis

[T] Started in summer 2001 just as a simple collection of
[T] celestial mechanics C++ classes, the ORSA project now
[T] collects many general classes, a graphical interface
[T] running under Linux/Unix, Mac OS X and Windows, and a
[T] number of tutorial programs.

[U] https://orsa.sourceforge.net/

